River Plate             1:1       Boca Juniors
Vélez Sarsfield         3:2       Estudiantes LP          at Ferro Carril Oeste


Independiente (A) won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:

Gimnasia y Esgrima LP: Rubén Busetti; Ricardo Freyre (81', sent out), Juan Bescos;
                       Pedro Irineo Peralta, Enrique Araujo, Juan Carlos Salzano;
                       Ricardo Balancini, Carlos Néstor Odoguardi (67', sent out),
                       Juan Antonucci, Enrique de la Vega, Horacio Heredia.

Independiente (A):     Eduardo Alberto López; Nito Osvaldo Veiga, 
                       Héctor Hugo Riera; Porfirio Emilio Arias, Gabriel Oscar Gil,
                       Ángel Lago; Roberto Berdia, Atilio Paramidani, 
                       Osvaldo Bianco, Juan Lorenzo, José Timmler.

Referee:               John Cox.

Field:                 Banfield.

Att.:                  900 tickets.

Goals:

